{"tid":1492934,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"8.21232425 有冇人知咩嚟？","createTime":"2019-08-21T05:00:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T05:52:09.000Z","uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"541139389c3b3f005017aff0167ff5a2ef2fc838","tid":1492934,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警方資訊<br />\n&amp;nbsp;<br />\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;警方收到市民申請，將於2019年8月24日在觀塘區一帶舉行公眾遊行及公眾集會。地點包括駿業街遊樂場、駿業街、海濱道、順業街、偉業街、常怡道及宏照道零碳天地一帶。<br />\n&amp;nbsp;<br />\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;鑑於近月進行公眾活動時，曾多次引發暴力衝擊事件，因此警方在必要時會展開驅散行動。市民如有需要，應關好窗戶並留在室內安全地方。如非必要，請勿前往相關地區。<br />\n&amp;nbsp;<br />\n&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;特此通知，以便及早作出相應安排。請密切留意警方發放的資訊及事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n                     秀茂坪警區指揮官示</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">對唔住做左標題黨</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但驅散行動又有咩好怕？<br />\n熱門一個PO都冇，邊有人出黎？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔該幫推行動PO</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UH5x6Mi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUH5x6Mi.png&h=21fa04ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/58gEMMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F58gEMMj.jpg&h=d9d6445a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4wGUAEF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4wGUAEF.jpg&h=67decb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cmOGZ6k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcmOGZ6k.jpg&h=2fc593d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGLVj6m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGLVj6m.jpg&h=26475986&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GyR9px2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGyR9px2.jpg&h=b5169eda&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"599e91a89c6ddab27e697edb1791f6da4fe09269","tid":1492934,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"fea702dc28e5c523c0b99aff8c93810e81045ac2","tid":1492934,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:01:51.000Z","msg":"唔係summer 緊咩"},{"pid":"740e369a4b7d525fe040e332f7d93786252b52ac","tid":1492934,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:02:03.000Z","msg":"人影都冇撚隻"},{"pid":"debaa44504ec1366ab490a20248843b97bb9089d","tid":1492934,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db50687f444c8d21ec915fe3c3ae7c5ff255515f","tid":1492934,"uid":143682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T05:52:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}